file_content.text: There's an inner palace. No ships left the planet--I'd guess the Masters are there.
You may defeat one, but all?
You will join us. We will break you and ruin your thoughts.
You will be part of our union, but in the depths of your despair and degradation, you will not save it.
We will all go mad together. Come!
Scout report says the palace doors are open. I think it's time.
I felt violence. Death. But you're alive.
And Lord Brontes has fallen back, but she and the others are still out there.
